<chapter id="introduction">
<title
>Ukwazisa</title>

<qandaset>
<qandaentry>
<question>
<para
>Yintoni i &kde;?</para>
</question>
<answer>
<para
>&kde; yiMeko-bume ye K Desktop. Yiprojekti equtshwe yi <ulink url="mailto:ettrich@kde.org"
>Matthias Ettrich</ulink
> ngo 1996.Injongo ye &kde; projekti is to connect the power of the &UNIX; operating systems with the comfort of a modern user interface.</para>
<para
>Ngokufutshane, &kde; izakuzisa &UNIX; kwi desktop!</para>
<para
>Ukuba ufuna ulwazi oluninzi malunga ne &kde;, jonga kwi <ulink url="http://www.kde.org/whatiskde/index.html"
>Yintoni i &kde;?</ulink
></para>
</answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question id="platform">
<para
>Ndingayilindela kowuphi umgangatho i &kde; ukusebenza?</para>
</question>
<answer>
<para
>&kde; yiMeko-bume yeDesktop yazo zonke ezithandwa yi &UNIX;. Ngexesha kuyinyaniso ukuba abaninzi &kde; ababhekisi phambili basebenzisa i &Linux;, &kde; yenza ngokumpuluswa kumqolo obanzi weendlela. Ungafuna, ngoko ke, ukutsala kabukhali ikhowudi yemvelaphi kancinane ukufumana i &kde; ukuqokelela kwenga-ziwayo-kakhulu eyahlekileyo ye &UNIX;,okanye ukuba awusebenzisi i &GNU; izixhobo zokubhekisa phambili, ingakumbi i &gcc; umqokeleli.</para>
<para
>Kuluhlu oluphantse lwagqitywa lweendlela &kde; isebenza kwi, nceda bhekisa ku <ulink url="http://promo.kde.org/kde_systems.php"
>olu mluhlu lwendlela ze KDE</ulink
> </para>
